    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Migrate the public RPC client naming to `Nvim.Client` and the generator naming to `Nvim.Client.Generator`.\n\n## Motivation\n\nThe current `NvimClient` naming is legacy and does not clearly separate the RPC client from generator tooling. Moving to `Nvim.Client` and `Nvim.Client.Generator` makes the package and namespace boundaries easier to understand before larger generator and publishing work.\n\n## Scope\n\n- Rename the RPC client namespace/package surface to `Nvim.Client`.\n- Rename the generator namespace/package surface to `Nvim.Client.Generator`.\n- Update project names, package metadata, documentation, examples, and generated code references where appropriate.\n- Preserve behaviour during the rename.\n- Leave the rplugin host in place for now; see #26 for the remote-plugin removal plan.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- RPC client code is exposed under `Nvim.Client`.\n- Generator code is exposed under `Nvim.Client.Generator`.\n- Documentation and examples use the new names.\n- Generated source compiles with the new namespace references.\n- Existing behaviour is preserved.\n\n## Blocked by\n\n- #31\n",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
