        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> * Rename the RPC client namespace/package surface to `Nvim.Client`.\n> * Rename the generator namespace/package surface to `Nvim.Client.Generator`.\n\nThere will only be one package. It can have multiple namespaces though.\n\n\n> Leave the rplugin host in place for now; see [simplify remote plugins #26](https://github.com/neovim/nvim.net/issues/26) for the remote-plugin removal plan.\n\n\nWe should just go ahead and rip out  the old \"remote plugin\" stuff. No need to continue pretending to support it.",
